    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i've talked to everyone. but they all say 'it gets better' or 'just hang in there' and it feels like they aren't even listening to what i'm actually saying. they don't understand that this isn't just a bad mood, it's my entire reality. every single second. it feels less like living and more like just enduring a punishment. it's exhausting to keep pretending that there's some kind of light at the end of this. sometimes it feels like the only way to actually stop the burning is to just... stop everything.",
